query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q2 s2 t2 tq2 u2 u1) NoHashJoin(a1 account q1 q2 s2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 s1) NoHashJoin(a1 account q1 q2 s1 s2 t2 tq2 u1 u2 t1) */ select count(account.display_name)
from question AS q2
inner join tag_question AS tq2
on tq2.question_id = q2.id
inner join tag AS t2
on tq2.tag_id = t2.id AND t2.name = 'nginx'
inner join so_user AS u2
on q2.owner_user_id = u2.id AND q2.site_id = u2.site_id
inner join site AS s2
on t2.site_id = s2.site_id AND q2.site_id = s2.site_id AND tq2.site_id = s2.site_id AND s2.site_name = 'serverfault'
inner join so_user AS u1
on u1.account_id = u2.account_id
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join question AS q1
on a1.site_id = q1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s1
on q1.site_id = s1.site_id AND s1.site_name = 'mathoverflow'
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.name like 'gr%'
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.site_id = s1.site_id AND tq1.question_id = q1.id AND tq1.tag_id = t1.id;
